1
00:00:44,085 --> 00:00:45,170
I'm sorry.

2
00:02:01,079 --> 00:02:02,122
Why?

3
00:02:04,582 --> 00:02:05,583
Jun-u,

4
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:08,336
I'll just go alone today.

5
00:02:10,713 --> 00:02:12,132
It's really okay.

6
00:02:14,175 --> 00:02:15,885
But I want to walk you home today.

7
00:02:18,179 --> 00:02:20,890
It's my birthday, and...

8
00:02:22,809 --> 00:02:24,310
I don't want to send you alone.

9
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:31,234
Okay.

10
00:02:53,715 --> 00:02:54,757
Go on in.

11
00:02:55,466 --> 00:02:57,719
Okay. Thanks for walking me home.

12
00:02:58,887 --> 00:03:00,930
I was worried you might get lost.

13
00:03:06,686 --> 00:03:09,188
I'm sorry about earlier.

14
00:03:09,939 --> 00:03:12,233
For saying that
without thinking about your feelings.

15
00:03:15,653 --> 00:03:16,738
Me too.

16
00:03:17,614 --> 00:03:18,781
I know how you feel.

17
00:03:18,865 --> 00:03:21,284
You were worried
I might be scolded by my mom.

18
00:03:21,826 --> 00:03:24,037
And whether my mom finds out or not,

19
00:03:24,329 --> 00:03:27,081
you just wanted to keep your promise.

20
00:03:31,544 --> 00:03:32,837
Thank you for today.

21
00:03:33,171 --> 00:03:36,132
It was the best birthday of my life.

22
00:03:37,050 --> 00:03:38,134
Really?

23
00:03:42,138 --> 00:03:43,181
See you.

24
00:03:43,514 --> 00:03:44,515
Okay.

25
00:03:53,316 --> 00:03:55,735
Jun-u, happy birthday.

26
00:03:56,361 --> 00:03:57,403
Thank you.

27
00:03:58,196 --> 00:03:59,239
You should go now.

28
00:04:15,463 --> 00:04:16,798
You're home early, Mom.

29
00:04:17,590 --> 00:04:18,633
Yes.

30
00:04:19,968 --> 00:04:21,886
My meeting ended early today.

31
00:04:24,681 --> 00:04:26,307
She wasn't waiting for me today.

32
00:04:27,141 --> 00:04:28,226
I know.

33
00:04:29,018 --> 00:04:30,728
I told her to quit.

34
00:04:31,312 --> 00:04:34,983
I thought about it, and it felt like
I was too harsh on you.

35
00:04:35,692 --> 00:04:37,485
And your grades improved this time.

36
00:04:38,486 --> 00:04:39,737
Mom, actually,

37
00:04:40,613 --> 00:04:43,366
today was Jun-u's birthday.

38
00:04:44,075 --> 00:04:47,245
I know I shouldn't have broken
the promise I made with you,

39
00:04:47,328 --> 00:04:49,497
but I wanted to celebrate his birthday,

40
00:04:49,831 --> 00:04:51,457
so I went to Jun-u's home.

41
00:04:51,666 --> 00:04:54,043
I begged her to let me go.

42
00:04:54,502 --> 00:04:55,920
I didn't go alone.

43
00:04:56,462 --> 00:04:57,880
I went with Chan-yeol, Da-huin,

44
00:04:58,673 --> 00:05:00,049
and everyone else.

45
00:05:00,717 --> 00:05:01,801
I'm sorry.

46
00:05:07,265 --> 00:05:09,809
You knew you shouldn't have
broken your promise.

47
00:05:10,435 --> 00:05:11,853
But why did you?

48
00:05:16,024 --> 00:05:17,567
Because I like Jun-u.

49
00:05:19,068 --> 00:05:21,946
From now on, I'll keep
all the promises I made with you.

50
00:05:22,030 --> 00:05:25,366
I'll attend the academy and
private lessons you found for me.

51
00:05:25,700 --> 00:05:27,410
And like you want...

52
00:05:29,704 --> 00:05:33,124
No, I'll do better on my own.

53
00:05:34,500 --> 00:05:35,585
Okay.

54
00:05:36,669 --> 00:05:37,754
Fine.

55
00:05:39,297 --> 00:05:41,549
You said you'd do better on your own.

56
00:05:46,012 --> 00:05:49,223
You have a math level test today,
but forget it if you don't want to.

57
00:05:51,768 --> 00:05:54,520
I'll take it.
Thank you for finding it for me.

58
00:05:54,604 --> 00:05:57,190
What time is the test?
I should get ready right away.

59
00:05:57,273 --> 00:05:58,316
Soo-bin.

60
00:06:01,277 --> 00:06:03,446
Take this. I know it's uncomfortable
without it.

61
00:06:16,209 --> 00:06:17,919
Song-hui, how have you been?

62
00:06:18,002 --> 00:06:20,421
Gosh, I called you several times,

63
00:06:20,505 --> 00:06:22,757
but you never called me back.
I was so disappointed.

64
00:06:22,840 --> 00:06:24,175
Oh, I was busy.

65
00:06:24,258 --> 00:06:26,677
I'm on my way to Seoul right now.

66
00:06:26,761 --> 00:06:30,098
I made some side dishes for you,
and I can drop by on the way.

67
00:06:30,181 --> 00:06:31,349
Shall I go to your company?

68
00:06:31,432 --> 00:06:33,267
No, I don't need side dishes.

69
00:06:33,351 --> 00:06:36,938
Yeon-u, I'm sorry but I'm a bit busy now,
so I have to go.

70
00:06:37,021 --> 00:06:38,564
Oh, I see.

71
00:06:38,648 --> 00:06:41,692
The thing is, today is Jun-u's birthday,

72
00:06:41,776 --> 00:06:43,361
so that's why I'm coming to Seoul.

73
00:06:44,195 --> 00:06:46,781
Okay, then. Call me later.

74
00:06:51,494 --> 00:06:53,121
-Happy birthday to you
-Happy birthday to you

75
00:06:54,789 --> 00:06:55,790
Here.

76
00:06:56,541 --> 00:06:58,835
How did you guys know?

77
00:06:59,001 --> 00:07:01,462
-Blow them out.
-Many happy returns.

78
00:07:01,546 --> 00:07:03,464
-Happy birthday.
-Congratulations.

79
00:07:04,632 --> 00:07:05,842
All right, then.

80
00:07:06,634 --> 00:07:08,010
Come on in!

81
00:07:25,820 --> 00:07:27,989
Yeon-u, can we meet?

82
00:07:50,052 --> 00:07:51,596
Look at this right here.

83
00:07:51,888 --> 00:07:53,055
Like this.

84
00:07:55,391 --> 00:07:56,434
Hello.

85
00:07:56,684 --> 00:07:58,895
Is Mr. Lee Jeong-min here?

86
00:07:59,061 --> 00:08:00,188
That's me.

87
00:08:00,354 --> 00:08:02,190
Mr. Oh sent me here.

88
00:08:02,273 --> 00:08:03,983
-Are you Choe Jun-u?
-Yes.

89
00:08:04,192 --> 00:08:05,359
It's nice to meet you.

90
00:08:06,068 --> 00:08:08,821
-Didn't it take so long to get here?
-No, it was okay.

91
00:08:09,071 --> 00:08:10,114
Come on in.

92
00:08:33,346 --> 00:08:35,139
Have you ever properly
learned to draw before?

93
00:08:36,390 --> 00:08:37,391
No.

94
00:08:38,017 --> 00:08:41,062
I just attended a small art academy
when I was little.

95
00:08:42,396 --> 00:08:44,690
You're really talented,
just like Han-gyeol said.

96
00:08:45,691 --> 00:08:47,610
Did you always like to draw?

97
00:08:48,361 --> 00:08:49,362
Yes.

98
00:08:49,987 --> 00:08:52,823
Since I was little,
I've always found doodling

99
00:08:53,199 --> 00:08:54,951
very comforting.

100
00:08:55,785 --> 00:08:57,537
I think it makes me happy.

101
00:08:58,162 --> 00:09:01,123
Nice, that's what I call talent.

102
00:09:02,166 --> 00:09:04,460
But preparing a portfolio
for college admission is not easy.

103
00:09:06,170 --> 00:09:08,381
Since you're starting late,
you'll have to work even harder.

104
00:09:08,464 --> 00:09:10,633
-No problem.
-Then shall we begin today?

105
00:09:10,716 --> 00:09:11,717
Sure.

106
00:09:18,766 --> 00:09:19,809
Jun-u.

107
00:09:20,851 --> 00:09:23,437
This part should be like this.

108
00:09:30,528 --> 00:09:31,571
Yeon-u.

109
00:09:33,406 --> 00:09:35,032
About Soo-bin and Jun-u...

110
00:09:36,158 --> 00:09:37,451
You knew, didn't you?

111
00:09:41,789 --> 00:09:44,125
Can I ask a big favor of you?

112
00:09:46,210 --> 00:09:47,795
What is it?

113
00:09:50,548 --> 00:09:51,882
Could you...

114
00:09:53,509 --> 00:09:56,887
transfer Jun-u to a school
in the city where you live?

115
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:01,601
Sorry?

116
00:10:02,184 --> 00:10:05,187
I don't think those two should be
left together in Seoul now.

117
00:10:06,314 --> 00:10:09,275
I considered moving Soo-bin
to a different school,

118
00:10:09,358 --> 00:10:11,694
but I can't do that because of my work.

119
00:10:12,903 --> 00:10:16,824
Wouldn't it be better for Jun-u
to live with you?

120
00:10:19,702 --> 00:10:20,786
Yeon-u, I know

121
00:10:20,870 --> 00:10:23,581
how selfish I must sound right now.
I'm fully aware of it.

122
00:10:23,664 --> 00:10:25,207
I'm really sorry. But when it comes

123
00:10:25,291 --> 00:10:28,628
to things that concern my child,
I can't be more understanding.

124
00:10:28,711 --> 00:10:30,379
I'm such a coward, aren't I?

125
00:10:36,218 --> 00:10:37,261
I'm sorry.

126
00:10:37,345 --> 00:10:41,599
But you see... Yeon-u, Soo-bin is...

127
00:10:42,516 --> 00:10:46,145
I'm suggesting this because I think
she really likes Jun-u.

128
00:10:46,395 --> 00:10:48,689
I think she likes him a lot.

129
00:10:50,274 --> 00:10:53,194
Girls at that age can fall
for someone very hard, you know.

130
00:10:53,486 --> 00:10:55,863
Even if you try to stop yourself,

131
00:10:55,946 --> 00:10:58,240
you can't really control
your feelings at that age.

132
00:10:58,949 --> 00:11:02,161
I know that Jun-u is a great guy

133
00:11:02,578 --> 00:11:04,747
because he takes after you.

134
00:11:04,830 --> 00:11:07,249
He's very kind. I know that.

135
00:11:08,459 --> 00:11:10,336
But as you know,

136
00:11:11,045 --> 00:11:13,923
they should focus on studying
more than anything at the moment.

137
00:11:14,632 --> 00:11:16,801
I'm sure you also want him

138
00:11:16,884 --> 00:11:19,512
to focus more on studying now.

139
00:11:23,933 --> 00:11:25,351
Yeon-u,

140
00:11:26,560 --> 00:11:28,813
let's split them up for the time being.

141
00:11:29,980 --> 00:11:30,981
Okay?

142
00:11:31,732 --> 00:11:35,069
We moms should put our feet down.
What else can we do?

143
00:11:37,780 --> 00:11:39,657
Yeon-u, I'm really...

144
00:11:40,991 --> 00:11:42,827
I'm really sorry.

145
00:11:43,244 --> 00:11:45,329
I'm so sorry,

146
00:11:45,538 --> 00:11:47,623
but I beg you.

147
00:11:48,624 --> 00:11:49,625
Please?

148
00:11:49,708 --> 00:11:52,461
I'm begging you. Please do it for me.

149
00:12:01,095 --> 00:12:05,057
Did you meet with Jun-u separately
by any chance?

150
00:12:12,857 --> 00:12:14,567
You didn't say anything

151
00:12:15,109 --> 00:12:17,445
that might have hurt his feelings,
did you?

152
00:12:35,045 --> 00:12:36,172
Song-hui.

153
00:12:37,673 --> 00:12:39,717
You're not the only mom in the world.

154
00:12:39,884 --> 00:12:41,427
I'm a mom too.

155
00:12:42,261 --> 00:12:44,638
I'm not as competent as you are,

156
00:12:44,722 --> 00:12:46,682
but I am a mother too.

157
00:12:47,683 --> 00:12:48,809
I, too,

158
00:12:49,852 --> 00:12:52,813
can do anything for my child.

159
00:12:52,897 --> 00:12:55,816
Nothing scares me if it's for my son.

160
00:12:56,275 --> 00:12:57,943
But you know what?

161
00:12:58,194 --> 00:13:00,196
I respect Jun-u's feelings.

162
00:13:01,530 --> 00:13:03,199
To me,

163
00:13:03,949 --> 00:13:07,286
his emotions are more important
than anything else

164
00:13:07,369 --> 00:13:08,621
in the world.

165
00:13:11,749 --> 00:13:15,419
Song-hui, listen.
I do not want to disrespect...

166
00:13:17,880 --> 00:13:19,798
or trample on his feelings.

167
00:13:33,646 --> 00:13:36,357
Soo-bin's mom hasn't found out
that you two are dating, right?

168
00:13:38,400 --> 00:13:39,401
No.

169
00:13:44,782 --> 00:13:45,783
Mr. Lee.

170
00:13:49,328 --> 00:13:51,413
-Mr. Lee.
-Yes.

171
00:13:52,248 --> 00:13:53,374
Well...

172
00:13:54,667 --> 00:13:56,544
I have to go to my part-time job.

173
00:13:56,627 --> 00:13:57,962
All right, Jun-u.

174
00:13:58,420 --> 00:14:00,839
But are you sure you can juggle this
with your part-time job?

175
00:14:01,590 --> 00:14:03,425
Of course. I can do it.

176
00:14:03,509 --> 00:14:05,678
I'll tidy up for you, so get going.

177
00:14:06,053 --> 00:14:08,347
Thank you. Bye.

178
00:14:29,410 --> 00:14:31,287
STUDENT RECORD
MA HWI-YEONG

179
00:14:31,370 --> 00:14:33,747
REPORT CARD

180
00:14:39,128 --> 00:14:41,297
-Hey, Jun-u!
-Mr. Oh.

181
00:14:41,505 --> 00:14:43,924
I had my first class at the academy
you put me in touch with.

182
00:14:44,008 --> 00:14:45,509
I see. How was it?

183
00:14:45,593 --> 00:14:47,845
-Did you do well?
-Yes.

184
00:14:47,928 --> 00:14:49,013
I'm glad to hear that.

185
00:14:49,179 --> 00:14:53,267
Jun-u, that instructor is
very good at what he does.

186
00:14:53,350 --> 00:14:55,311
So just follow his instructions

187
00:14:55,519 --> 00:14:57,313
and do your best.

188
00:14:57,688 --> 00:14:59,148
Don't worry about anything.

189
00:14:59,231 --> 00:15:00,858
Okay, I'll do my best.

190
00:15:01,692 --> 00:15:04,904
Oh, and I really wanted to thank you.

191
00:15:05,237 --> 00:15:07,156
I'm hugely...

192
00:15:11,368 --> 00:15:12,411
What? Go on.

193
00:15:13,746 --> 00:15:14,997
I'm hugely indebted to you.

194
00:15:19,710 --> 00:15:22,880
Oh, okay. My goodness.

195
00:15:24,465 --> 00:15:26,717
Don't be silly.

196
00:15:27,134 --> 00:15:29,428
-Are you going to work now?
-Yes.

197
00:15:30,512 --> 00:15:32,139
All right. Work hard.

198
00:15:33,223 --> 00:15:36,018
And try to get some studying done
whenever you have a chance.

199
00:15:38,103 --> 00:15:39,104
Okay.

200
00:15:50,741 --> 00:15:51,742
LETTER OF APOLOGY
CHOE JUN-U

201
00:15:52,868 --> 00:15:56,038
So this is... It's a case of forced...

202
00:15:56,121 --> 00:15:57,289
A forced transfer, sir.

203
00:15:57,373 --> 00:15:58,666
Lower your voice.

204
00:15:58,749 --> 00:15:59,750
You're...

205
00:16:01,085 --> 00:16:02,920
I'm surprised.

206
00:16:03,337 --> 00:16:06,131
You have a talent. You did
a great job of drawing this ladybug.

207
00:16:19,478 --> 00:16:20,938
I'm sorry I'm late.

208
00:16:33,659 --> 00:16:36,370
SELF-MADE CEO BRIBES HIS SON'S TEACHER

209
00:17:17,244 --> 00:17:19,079
CHOE JUN-U

210
00:17:38,432 --> 00:17:40,768
Happy birthday, Jun-u.

211
00:17:41,310 --> 00:17:44,772
No one's birthday has ever felt

212
00:17:44,855 --> 00:17:46,148
this important to me.

213
00:17:46,398 --> 00:17:47,900
-Let me do it.
-Hurry up.

214
00:17:47,983 --> 00:17:50,694
-Give it to me. No, wait!
-I'm done.

215
00:17:50,778 --> 00:17:52,321
-Where? It looks fine.
-Gosh.

216
00:17:52,488 --> 00:17:54,239
-Let's just wrap it like this.
-It's not ripped.

217
00:17:54,323 --> 00:17:56,492
I always thought it was such a clichÃ©

218
00:17:56,658 --> 00:17:58,869
to thank someone
for being born into this world,

219
00:17:58,952 --> 00:18:00,829
but you taught me
that one could truly mean it.

220
00:18:01,497 --> 00:18:04,458
Jun-u, thank you for being born
into this world.

221
00:18:04,583 --> 00:18:08,003
You're the most precious person to me.

222
00:18:08,545 --> 00:18:11,423
You've finally found your path,
so I prepared this for you.

223
00:18:11,757 --> 00:18:13,884
But the thing is,
I know nothing about art.

224
00:18:14,093 --> 00:18:16,887
I'm not sure if this is right.

225
00:18:17,221 --> 00:18:19,890
I hope you like the gift
even if I got it wrong.

226
00:18:20,224 --> 00:18:21,517
To Choe Jun-u.

227
00:18:22,142 --> 00:18:23,310
From Soo-bin.

228
00:18:23,811 --> 00:18:25,270
It can never be wrong

229
00:18:25,771 --> 00:18:27,022
if it's from you.

230
00:18:32,861 --> 00:18:33,946
Jun-u.

231
00:18:35,322 --> 00:18:36,782
Jun-u.

232
00:18:37,407 --> 00:18:38,408
Mom?

233
00:18:38,742 --> 00:18:40,160
Thanks for the food.

234
00:18:45,374 --> 00:18:47,000
-Is it good?
-Yes.

235
00:18:47,960 --> 00:18:51,171
But you shouldn't eat
right before you go to bed.

236
00:18:52,714 --> 00:18:55,175
I skipped dinner, so I was hungry anyway.

237
00:18:56,718 --> 00:18:58,887
Today is a very special day.

238
00:18:58,971 --> 00:19:00,848
It's your birthday,

239
00:19:00,931 --> 00:19:02,933
and it was your first day
at the art academy.

240
00:19:03,392 --> 00:19:06,353
Actually, Mr. Oh was a big help.

241
00:19:07,312 --> 00:19:09,481
He found an academy for me

242
00:19:09,565 --> 00:19:12,484
and put in a word for me
so I wouldn't be burdened.

243
00:19:13,360 --> 00:19:16,780
I know. We owe him a lot.
How should we repay him?

244
00:19:17,030 --> 00:19:18,407
I'll have to work harder.

245
00:19:24,204 --> 00:19:25,164
Mom.

246
00:19:27,958 --> 00:19:29,209
After all,

247
00:19:30,252 --> 00:19:32,796
I met many good people at this school.

248
00:19:35,424 --> 00:19:37,009
Mr. Oh...

249
00:19:37,801 --> 00:19:38,802
and...

250
00:19:45,642 --> 00:19:47,144
You also met Soo-bin?

251
00:19:55,402 --> 00:19:56,486
Well...

252
00:19:58,780 --> 00:20:03,076
You didn't say anything that might
have hurt his feelings, did you?

253
00:20:07,039 --> 00:20:10,125
My mom still thinks that the time
she spent with her first love

254
00:20:10,542 --> 00:20:13,462
years ago was the most
beautiful moment in her life.

255
00:20:13,879 --> 00:20:16,840
Back when she was 18.
She still misses that moment.

256
00:20:19,092 --> 00:20:20,844
You have something to tell me, don't you?

257
00:20:21,428 --> 00:20:22,930
No, I don't.

258
00:20:25,974 --> 00:20:28,852
Are you sure? I think you do.

259
00:20:32,439 --> 00:20:33,440
Jun-u.

260
00:20:34,650 --> 00:20:37,819
You've grown up to be
such a kind, thoughtful boy.

261
00:20:38,195 --> 00:20:40,739
Thank you for being my son.

262
00:20:47,037 --> 00:20:48,163
Eat up.

263
00:20:48,413 --> 00:20:49,414
Okay.

264
00:21:18,485 --> 00:21:20,570
I wonder if he liked my present.

265
00:21:22,531 --> 00:21:23,657
I miss him.

